rue','B00TNC1OJW','POSITIVE'),(402,4,'Good Products','https://www.amazon.in/gp/customer-reviews/R2K8A78UWOVQ75/ref=cm_cr_arp_d_rvw_ttl?ie=UTF8&ASIN=B00TNC1OJW','Reviewed in India on 14 July 2024','Good products','True','B00TNC1OJW','POSITIVE'),(403,5,'Awesome product. High quality and sturdy','https://www.amazon.in/gp/customer-reviews/R3R7MJBE5HRHUD/ref=cm_cr_arp_d_rvw_ttl?ie=UTF8&ASIN=B01AUPGA9Y','Reviewed in India on 23 August 2017','Awesome product.High quality and sturdy. Perfect for professional use.Eventhough the product is excellent still many users are reviewing it to negative as far as leakage is concerned. It is because of the ignorance while assembling the extension pipe provided in the pack. Manufacturer has given several O ring rubber washers in a separate pouch but it seems most of the buyers are  manifesting that as a mere additional accessory which may not be useful for its regular use.But it is totally wrong.There is a cap provided in the pack for attaching the extension pipe with the water injector module .It has to be tightened after inserting the O ring washer in between. Otherwise water leakage from the joint is a most probable outcome.Once the washer is attached the unit will perform flawless.Perhaps a common user may not recognize the importance of  an O ring washer in  water supply.It can be visible in our home plumbing .From a wash basin to an electric geyser the role of washers are not so least.Even the jaguar Taps will start to leak between the tap and the tube connecting to the mains line  without an O ring .This product deserves nothing less than 5 stars and those who gave less than 5 stars for reasons other than leakage have overlooked the product.Since it is a pressure sprayer designed for  watering and spraying pesticides to plants and not  to replace any pressure wash for cleaning cars or algae. Every product is expected to perform some function and never discontent with that only because it is not performing some other function.This is purely a manual pressure sprayer designed to sprinkle pesticide or water at a nominal pressure and for the same purpose 120 or 140 bar is not at all required.It cannot be used to clean vehicle as the pressure is not at all sufficient for self cleaning without wiping.','True','B01AUPGA9Y','POSITIVE'),(404,4,'Intended for Rooftop gardeners','https://www.amazon.in/gp/customer-reviews/R2VT3423H73H3D/ref=cm_cr_arp_d_rvw_ttl?ie=UTF8&ASIN=B01AUPGA9Y','Reviewed in India on 28 August 2022','If you have 150-200 pots to feed liquid nutrients, this is the best option for you. But for 600 pot owners, I would suggest a full 16 litre sprayer. I have to feed at least 9-10 litres of liquid to my plants time to time, so I preferred this 8 litre sprayer, which is light weight and easy to carry. Kissankraft sprayer comes with two types of carrying system. One can hang it from soldier by strap or can carry by handle. I prefer the second one. The pumper has a locking system and locked pumper becomes carrying handle. The sprayer nozzle and pipe can cover 5 feet radius, so positioning it nearby a set of pots, drenching them and carrying it in another spot is less tiresome than all time carrying it by strap.Pumper is very easy going. At least 30-32 push is necessary in a set and you have to repeat it a few times to spray full 8 litre. Nozzle rod is made of plastic, light weight and sturdy. Same is true for the body parts.There is a convenient pressure release valve and a sprayer push lock to continue spraying without a fatigued finger.I found many reviews complaining about leakage although did not experienced any. I did not used spare valves provided with it, just tightened parts before using, and it working fine. Flow is flawless.Only negative side is, this pumper does not comes with an extended base. So best keep it for rooftop gardening. If one has a small kitchen garden in backyard with jagged land it would be difficult to keep pumper in upright position while spraying.','True','B01