.amazon.in/gp/customer-reviews/R1P74F3AYGDJQE/ref=cm_cr_arp_d_rvw_ttl?ie=UTF8&ASIN=B01AUPGA9Y','Reviewed in India on 26 August 2021','Quality of the overall product is comparable to cheaper chinese versions. The main container is sturdy and looks durable but almost all moving parts (pump, valves, sprayer handle etc) are fragile. Gaskets have started leaking after light use 3 to 4 times in just two weeks, luckily a spare set was provided with the pump. Suitable for domestic use with sanitizers etc but not suggested for pesticides or farm/orchard use. Overall not a very bad product for light domestic use.','True','B01AUPGA9Y','NEGATIVE'),(408,4,'Good','https://www.amazon.in/gp/customer-reviews/R2SSXYPYCV3CB8/ref=cm_cr_arp_d_rvw_ttl?ie=UTF8&ASIN=B01AUPGA9Y','Reviewed in India on 10 April 2024','Ok quality good useful for home garden','True','B01AUPGA9Y','POSITIVE'),(409,5,'Washing Two Wheelers and AC is easier and cheaper','https://www.amazon.in/gp/customer-reviews/R2ARCDFDUJQHX8/ref=cm_cr_arp_d_rvw_ttl?ie=UTF8&ASIN=B01AUPGA9Y','Reviewed in India on 19 May 2023','The media could not be loaded.\n                I live in apartment with very dusty parking in basement with no water tap. My bike (Unicorn 150) and Scooter (Jupiter 125-19 Features more than Latest Activas) gets too much dust. The day I received this Kisan Kraft 8 liter manual sprayer, I was very happy and surprised that in just 8 liter of water, I can clean my bike completely by self and avoid standing in queue at washing station. My only regret is, I should have ordered it years ago (LOL I didn\'t knew when this product entered market). Just fill 8 liter of water and pump 20 times. If you feel pressure is not good then pump again few more times and spray clean. Repeat the cycle until water is no more. For me it takes 3 cycle of 20 times pump. I first adjust the nozzle to sprinkle and wet my bike. Wait for 5 min. Then I adjust the nozzle to thin water pressure to pressure wash my bike. Some times I first sprinkle water and then take a coir brush and shampoo (Sunsilk Rs. 1 packet) and rub over my bike. Then I pressure wash. That\'s all in 8 liter of water. Its almost a miracle. Amazing product!!!This Rs. 1000 product could literally save many thousands.I also washed the outdoor and indoor unit of my AC and my god I never imagined the amount of dust was in there. My entire floor was almost black as the dust got mixed with water. That was crazy. Now even at 29c + Ceiling fan at medium speed, my AC gives hill station feeling in Summer. Again Amazing manual pressure washer!!!Bonus tips:1. After using, untight the handle in by 10% to prevent damage to the rubber O ring. If you ask why, answer is, if product is not in use and you screw it tightly then the rubber O rings may damage being subjected to constant pressure.2. Sprinkle with nozzle just 1cm away from the fins when cleaning AC\'s internal unit.3. Use sprinkle to clean mosquito net.','True','B01AUPGA9Y','POSITIVE'),(410,2,'Sprayer not functioning within 15 days of purchase','https://www.amazon.in/gp/customer-reviews/R23K2XV8G4XBR1/ref=cm_cr_arp_d_rvw_ttl?ie=UTF8&ASIN=B01AUPGA9Y','Reviewed in India on 16 March 2024','It\'s a china productNo issuesBut the sprayer is not working properlyCalled customer care but no proper responseEmailed alsoGot the numbers of the service person inumbaiBut still no parts reached or deliveredVery sad to buy this product','True','B01AUPGA9Y','NEGATIVE'),(411,4,'Good','https://www.amazon.in/gp/customer-reviews/R9S8EEDAL38HD/ref=cm_cr_arp_d_rvw_ttl?ie=UTF8&ASIN=B01AUPGA9Y','Reviewed in India on 3 January 2024','Nice','True','B01AUPGA9Y','POSITIVE'),(412,4,'Good','https://www.amazon.in/gp/customer-reviews/RZHBYQIBQYNW0/ref=cm_cr_arp_d_rvw_ttl?ie=UTF8&ASIN=B01AUPGA9Y','Reviewed in India on 16 December 2023','Good','True','B01AUPGA9Y','POSITIVE'),(413,5,'Excellent quality.','https://www.amazon.in/gp/customer-reviews/RI9FLMTFYIQJZ/ref=cm_cr_arp_d_rvw_ttl?ie=UTF8&ASIN=B07XP89S1Z','Reviewed in India