elp Fertilizer:Source: Extracts from seaweed or kelp.Benefits: Rich in trace minerals, seaweed fertilizer enhances plant growth, improves stress resistance, and promotes overall plant health.Cover Crops:Source: Various plants grown to cover and protect the soil.Benefits: Leguminous cover crops, like clover, add nitrogen to the soil through a process called nitrogen fixation. Cover crops also prevent erosion and improve soil fertility.Green Manure:Source: Plants, such as legumes, that are grown and then plowed back into the soil.Benefits: Adds organic matter, improves soil structure, and releases nutrients as it decomposes.When using organic fertilizers, it\'s important to note that they release nutrients more slowly compared to synthetic fertilizers. Patience is key, as organic fertilizers contribute to long-term soil health and sustainability. Additionally, the choice of organic fertilizer may depend on the specific nutrient needs of the plants and the soil conditions. Always follow recommended application rates to avoid over-fertilizing.','True','B08D8CHZ9C','POSITIVE'),(3579,3,'Fertiliser is not good for plants','https://www.amazon.in/gp/customer-reviews/R1MIVWVPW0BG2Y/ref=cm_cr_arp_d_rvw_ttl?ie=UTF8&ASIN=B08D8CHZ9C','Reviewed in India on 8 July 2024','Waste of money.','True','B08D8CHZ9C','NEGATIVE'),(3580,5,'It\'s good for growth of my plant','https://www.amazon.in/gp/customer-reviews/ROSHU7S2AKR1Z/ref=cm_cr_arp_d_rvw_ttl?ie=UTF8&ASIN=B08D8CHZ9C','Reviewed in India on 7 May 2024','I brought this format plants good growth','True','B08D8CHZ9C','POSITIVE'),(3581,4,'Best for plant','https://www.amazon.in/gp/customer-reviews/R239B4YSKHVCOK/ref=cm_cr_arp_d_rvw_ttl?ie=UTF8&ASIN=B08D8CHZ9C','Reviewed in India on 10 March 2024','It\'s really good','True','B08D8CHZ9C','POSITIVE'),(3582,1,'Appears to city waste compost Not vermi compost','https://www.amazon.in/gp/customer-reviews/R2MBM6RVGB21B5/ref=cm_cr_arp_d_rvw_ttl?ie=UTF8&ASIN=B08D8CHZ9C','Reviewed in India on 21 June 